{"lemma":"بَرِّيِّي","slug":"بَرِّيِّي","root":"ب.ر.ر","root_slug":"ب-ر-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ر-ر","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2148","n2149","n2165","n2422","n2428","n2432"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%91%D9%8A%D9%90%D9%91%D9%8A"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"wild"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"overland, land, terrestrial"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"بَرّ (barr, “land”) + ـِيّ (-iyy)."},"ipa":["/bar.riː/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2148","headword_ar":"بُرَّى","root":"br","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A good, sweet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasant, word"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"expression"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saying:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bir~N","text_ar":"بِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ benevolent and solicitous regard or treatment or conduct. ” (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]},{"entry_id":"n2149","headword_ar":"بَرِّىٌّ","root":"br","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"belonging to,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"relating to, the land"},{"kind":"text","text":"as opposed to the sea or a great river. ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"belonging to,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"relating to, the desert"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waste; growing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"living,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"produced, in the desert"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waste; wild,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in an uncultivated state."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b3-  And hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN bar~iy~apN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ بَرِّيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Uncultivated land; without seed-produce, and unfruitful; without green herbs"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leguminous plants and without waters; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyfiy~apN","text_ar":"رِيفِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IAar, M, K. *) And, simply, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bar~ay~apN","text_ar":"بَرَّيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bar~iytN","text_ar":"بَرِّيتٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A'Obeyd, IAar, Sh, S, K,) the latter a variation of the former, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"being made quiescent, and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"therefore being changed into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiforiytN","text_ar":"عِفْرِيتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiforiyapN","text_ar":"عِفْرِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) a rel. n. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bar~N","text_ar":"بَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sh, T, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A desert; a waste; a spacious tract of ground without herbage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHoraA='u","text_ar":"صَحْرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, M, A, Msb, K:) [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bar~N","text_ar":"بَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a tract nearer to the desert"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albar~","text_ar":"البَرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"than it is to water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, T:) [but some write the latter word ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bir~iytN","text_ar":"بِرِّيتٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and it is said that]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bir~iytu","text_ar":"بِرِّيتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brt","text_ar":"برت"},{"kind":"text","text":",) of the same measure as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sik~iytN","text_ar":"سِكِّيتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K in that art.,) signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flat, even,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"level, land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a barren, flat, even,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"level, land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"a poet says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"bir~iytu A^aroDK baEodahaA bir~iytu"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A barren, flat land, after which is a"},{"kind":"text","text":"second"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"barren, flat land"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (T:) ISd says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bir~iytN","text_ar":"بِرِّيتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in a poem of Ru-beh, [from which the ex. given above is probably taken,] is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEoliytN","text_ar":"فِعْلِيتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albar~u","text_ar":"البَرُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and that art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brt","text_ar":"برت"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not the place in which it should be mentioned: (TA:) Lth says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albar~iytu","text_ar":"البَرِّيتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a noun derived from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albar~iy~apu","text_ar":"البَرِّيَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"becoming quiescent, and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"becoming an inseparable"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":", as though it were a radical letter, as in the case of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiforiyapN","text_ar":"عِفْرِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which thus becomes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiforiytN","text_ar":"عِفْرِيتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"br~y~p","text_ar":"برّيّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraAriY~u","text_ar":"بَرَارِىُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and that of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"br~yt","text_ar":"برّيت"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraAriytu","text_ar":"بَرَارِيتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","A","Msb","K","Sh","T","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n2165","headword_ar":"بَرِيَ","root":"brA^","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. generally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buro'N","text_ar":"بُرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA='apN","text_ar":"بَرَا=ءَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"free,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of, or from, a thing; in the manners which will be explained below: (Bd ii. 51:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, in a state of freedom"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"immunity, secure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"safe."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy^a mina AlmaraDi","text_ar":"بَرِيَ مِنَ المَرَضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA^a","text_ar":"بَرَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baruw^a","text_ar":"بَرُوَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buro'N","text_ar":"بُرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy^a mn AlmrD","text_ar":"بَرِيَ من المرض"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buro'N","text_ar":"بُرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm; and the people of El-Hijáz say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA^a","text_ar":"بَرَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baro'N","text_ar":"بَرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h: (S:) accord. to As,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariYa mn","text_ar":"بَرِىَ من"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmrD","text_ar":"المرض"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of the dial. of Temeem; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA^a","text_ar":"بَرَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the dial. of the people of El-Hijáz: or, accord. to AZ, the people of El-Hijáz say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA^a","text_ar":"بَرَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the rest of the Arabs say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy^a","text_ar":"بَرِيَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA^a","text_ar":"بَرَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[alone], said of a sick man, aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy^a","text_ar":"بَرِيَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baruw^a","text_ar":"بَرُوَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baro'N","text_ar":"بَرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[probably a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buro'N","text_ar":"بُرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruw^N","text_ar":"بُرُوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, accord. to Lh, the people of El- Hijáz say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA^a","text_ar":"بَرَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buro'N","text_ar":"بُرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruw^N","text_ar":"بُرُوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruwo'N","text_ar":"بُرُوْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and the people of El-'Áliyeh, ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA^a","text_ar":"بَرَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buro'N","text_ar":"بُرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruw^u","text_ar":"بُرُوُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and Temeem,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy^a","text_ar":"بَرِيَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buro'N","text_ar":"بُرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruw^N","text_ar":"بُرُوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA^a","text_ar":"بَرَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) said by IKtt to be the most chaste form, (TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) agreeably with analogy, (TA,) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) said by Zj to be the only instance of a verb of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEala","text_ar":"فَعَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"for its last radical letter having its aor. of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yafoEulu","text_ar":"يَفْعُلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [though others mention also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraA^a","text_ar":"قَرَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaqoruw^u","text_ar":"يَقْرُوُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hanaA^a","text_ar":"هَنَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yahonuw^u","text_ar":"يَهْنُوُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] and asserted to be a bad form, (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buro'N","text_ar":"بُرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruwo'N","text_ar":"بُرُوْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baruw^a","text_ar":"بَرُوَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) not a chaste form, (TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy^a","text_ar":"بَرِيَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) a chaste form, (TA,) [and the most common of all,] aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baro'N","text_ar":"بَرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruw^N","text_ar":"بُرُوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buro'N","text_ar":"بُرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (CK,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruwo'N","text_ar":"بُرُوْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became free from the disease, sickness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"malady:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he recovered from it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became convalescent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"healthy, at the close of disease, but was yet weak; or he recovered, but not completely, his health and strength;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"niqaha","text_ar":"نِقَهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;) i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he acquired that slight degree of soundness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"health, which comes at the close of disease, but with disease remaining in him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy^a","text_ar":"بَرِيَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljuroju","text_ar":"الجُرْجُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA^a","text_ar":"بَرَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The wound healed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became in a healing state:"},{"kind":"text","text":"of frequent occurrence.] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy^a mina AlA^amori","text_ar":"بَرِيَ مِنَ الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [the only form of the verb used in this case, and in the other cases in which it is mentioned below,] aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", the latter extr., (M, K,) or rather it is very strange, for IKoot says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEima","text_ar":"نَعِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yanoEumu","text_ar":"يَنْعُمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faDila","text_ar":"فَضِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yafoDulu","text_ar":"يَفْضُلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", are the only instances of this kind, (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA='apN","text_ar":"بَرَا=ءَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA='N","text_ar":"بَرَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruw^N","text_ar":"بُرُوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buro'N","text_ar":"بُرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruwo'N","text_ar":"بُرُوْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (CK;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tbr~A^","text_ar":"تبرّا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, * M, K, Mgh; *) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, free from the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quit, thereof; clear of having"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of having had"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taken, any part therein; guiltless of it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"irresponsible for it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in an ex. q. v. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiDaADN","text_ar":"عِضَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] said in relation to [a fault or the like, and] a debt, and a claim, and religion [&c.]. (Lh, M.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy^a mina AlEayobi","text_ar":"بَرِيَ مِنَ العَيْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEuyuwbi","text_ar":"العُيُوبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA='apN","text_ar":"بَرَا=ءَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, free"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the fault, defect, imperfection, blemish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vice"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Mgh, Msb,) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"faults,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy^a mina Ald~ayoni","text_ar":"بَرِيَ مِنَ الدَّيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, Mgh, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~uyuwni","text_ar":"الدُّيُونِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA='apN","text_ar":"بَرَا=ءَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quit, of the debt;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"debts;"},{"kind":"text","text":"S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"irresponsible for it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state of immunity with respect to it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exempt from the demand thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bary^a","text_ar":"بَريَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilayoka mino Haq~ika","text_ar":"اـِلَيْكَ مِنْ حَقِّكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA='apN","text_ar":"بَرَا=ءَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA='N","text_ar":"بَرَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, M) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruw^N","text_ar":"بُرُوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quit, to thee, of thy claim,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"due,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"right;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exempt from the demand thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tbr~A^","text_ar":"تبرّا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy^otu A_ilayoka mino fulaAnK","text_ar":"بَرِيْتُ اـِلَيْكَ مِنْ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA='pN","text_ar":"بَرَا=ءةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have become, clear, to thee, of having"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of having had"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taken, any part with such a one;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"irresponsible to thee for such a one:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (AZ, T, S: * [in one copy of the S, I find the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy^otu minoka","text_ar":"بَرِيْتُ مِنْكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", commencing the art.; but not in other copies:]) this is the only form of the verb used in this case, and in relation to debt [and the like]. (AZ, T.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He removed himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kept, far,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"aloof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[from unclean things, or things occasioning blame; followed by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino","text_ar":"مِنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with which it may be rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he shunned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"avoided;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tanaz~ahu","text_ar":"تَنَزَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabaAEada","text_ar":"تَبَاعَدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T.) [You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy^a mina","text_ar":"بَرِيَ مِنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aqo*aAri","text_ar":"الاَقْذَارِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He removed himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kept, far,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"aloof, from unclean things."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He manifested an excuse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asserted himself to be clear"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quit"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"irresponsible,"},{"kind":"text","text":"like ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tbr~A^","text_ar":"تبرّا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and gave warning;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEo*ara","text_ar":"اَعْذَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano*ara","text_ar":"اَنْذَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T.) Hence, in the Kur [ix. 1],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA='apN mina A@ll~`hi warasuwlihi","text_ar":"بَرَا=ءَةٌ مِنَ ا@للّٰهِ وَرَسُولِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A manifestation of excuse, and a warning, from God and his apostle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA^a A@ll~`hu Alxaloqa","text_ar":"بَرَاَ ا@للّٰهُ الخَلْقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, T, S, M, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxaliyaqapa","text_ar":"الخَلِيَقَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, M, &c.,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baro'N","text_ar":"بَرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruwo'N","text_ar":"بُرُوْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, Lh, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God created mankind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the beings,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"things, that are created,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalaqa","text_ar":"خَلَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, T, M, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after no similitude,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"model,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but,"},{"kind":"text","text":"properly, though not always meaning so,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"out of pre-existing matter;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for] Bd says [in ii. 51] that the primary meaning of the root"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"br'","text_ar":"برء"},{"kind":"text","text":"is to denote a thing's becoming clear, or free, of, or from, another thing; either by being released [therefrom], as in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy^a AlmariyDu","text_ar":"بَرِيَ المَرِيضُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino maraDihi","text_ar":"مِنْ مَرَضِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almadoyuwnu mino daynihi","text_ar":"المَدْيُونُ مِنْ دَينِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[both sufficiently explained above]; or by production [therefrom], as in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA^a A@ll~`hu A=dama mina AlT~iyni","text_ar":"بَرَاَ ا@للّٰهُ ا=دَمَ مِنَ الطِّينِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God produced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"created, Adam, from,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"out of, clay"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) This verb relates to substances [as in the exs. given above] and to accidents; and hence, [in the Kur lvii. 22,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino qboli A^ano naboraA^ahaA","text_ar":"مِنْ قبْلِ اَنْ نَبْرَاَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Before our creating it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"if"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hA","text_ar":"ها"},{"kind":"text","text":"refer to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muSiybap","text_ar":"مُصِيبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", preceding it; but, as Bd says, it may refer to this, or to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aroD","text_ar":"الاَرْض"},{"kind":"text","text":", or to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anofus","text_ar":"اَنْفُس"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (M:) but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albaro'u","text_ar":"البَرْءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has a more particular application than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxaloqu","text_ar":"الخَلْقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the former being particularly applied to the creation of animate beings, with few exceptions: you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA^a A@ll~`hu Aln~asamapa","text_ar":"بَرَاَ ا@للّٰهُ النَّسَمَةَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa xalaqa Als~am`waAti waAlA^aroDa","text_ar":"وَ خَلَقَ السَّمٰوَاتِ وَالاَرْضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God created,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"produced, man,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the soul, and He created the heavens and the earth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) [To this verb, or perhaps to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baray","text_ar":"بَرَي"},{"kind":"text","text":", or to both,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"בָּרָ","text_ar":"בָּרָ","orth_type":"plain"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the Hebrew equivalent, properly (though not necessarily always) signifying “ he created out of pre-existing matter, ” or “ he fashioned. ”]"}],"source_refs":["T","Msb","S","M","K","TA","CK","Lh","Mgh","Fr","AZ"]},{"entry_id":"n2422","headword_ar":"بَرَى","root":"brY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (T, M, K,) first pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barayotu","text_ar":"بَرَيْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroYN","text_ar":"بَرْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He formed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fashioned, by cutting; shaped out;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pared;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, T, M, K;) a reed for writing, (Lth, As, ISk, T, S, M, Msb,) and a stick, or piece of wood, (Lth, T, M,) and an arrow, (M, K,) &c.; (M;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbtrY","text_ar":"ابترى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barawotu","text_ar":"بَرَوْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lth, T,) is a dial. var., (Msb,) used by some, who say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huma yaqoluw Albur~a","text_ar":"هُمَ يَقْلُو البُرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaqoliY","text_ar":"يَقْلِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Lth, T.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (As, T,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (As, T, M, K,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fatigued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"jaded, and made to lose flesh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, * T, * S,) a she-camel, (As, T,) or a camel: (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(journeying)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered"},{"kind":"text","text":"him"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"emaciated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) and in like manner one says of a year of dearth or drought. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barayotu sanaAmahaA bisayoriY EalayohaA","text_ar":"بَرَيْتُ سَنَامَهَا بِسَيْرِى عَلَيْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I wasted her hump by my journeying upon her"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: occurring in a poem of El-Aashà. (M.)       -A2-  See also 3: ―         -b2-  and see 5, in two places."}],"source_refs":["T","M","K","S","Msb","Lth","As","ISk"]},{"entry_id":"n2428","headword_ar":"بَرًى","root":"brY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barFA","text_ar":"بَرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brw","text_ar":"برو"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n2432","headword_ar":"بَرِىٌّ","root":"brY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", applied to an arrow,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maboriY~N","text_ar":"مَبْرِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Formed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fashioned, by cutting; shaped out;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pared"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (T, M, K;) or (M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"completely;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but not feathered, nor headed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"for an arrow when first cut is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiToEN","text_ar":"قِطْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then it is formed, or fashioned, by cutting, or shaped out, or pared, and is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariY~N","text_ar":"بَرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and when straightened, and fit to be feathered and headed, it is a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qidoH","text_ar":"قِدْح"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and when feathered and headed, it becomes a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sahom","text_ar":"سَهْم"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T.)       -A2-  It is also sometimes used for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariYo'N","text_ar":"بَرِىْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Kz, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brA^","text_ar":"برا"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["M","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}